            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1656425439540-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roll your <strong>lime[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Combine your <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>red chilli relish</strong>,<strong> half </strong>your<strong> soy sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!),<strong> </strong>the juice of the <strong>lime[s]</strong>, a splash of <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626950916301-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626950916301-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626950916301-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626950916301-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1626950916301-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free mince has started to brown, add your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, the <strong>remaining soy sauce </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 2-3 min or until the meat-free mince has cooked through – this is your <strong>sticky meat-free mince</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626950919873-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626950919873-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626950919873-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626950919873-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1626950919873-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate</p><p>Put the plate in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 1-2 min, or until the tortillas are warmed through</p><p>Add most of the<strong> satay sauce</strong> (save some for later!) to the <strong>sticky meat-free  mince</strong> and mix until well coated</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627985498136-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627985498136-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627985498136-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627985498136-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1627985498136-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>sticky meat-free mince </strong>between the <strong>warmed tortillas </strong>and top with the<strong> grated carrot</strong> and<strong> cucumber batons</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>remaining satay sauce</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
